{"tid":1466580,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔割！ 射核彈都唔割！","createTime":"2019-08-13T16:48:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:00:56.000Z","uid":240360,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"01b50a8f56235dd78c55fa79d34b03f0b27ccd2b","tid":1466580,"uid":240360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:48:45.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山，各有各做！<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">不篤灰！<br />\n不割蓆！<br />\n不分化</span></span><br />\n各位千祈唔好中計！！<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04ba2a982d3ea1cc08942327e447b3e7213547c8","tid":1466580,"uid":267435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:49:04.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7ff16318cb0ea9ee4fc1971eb0a642be6169866","tid":1466580,"uid":240360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:49:12.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"e4e612b44c63200a8f809c61c16f1ab74814767b","tid":1466580,"uid":240360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:49:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"35b1ffbdbf3c26930bac50fdf0ec495c5dc9b94b","tid":1466580,"uid":41875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:49:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">失敗主義</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">解散軍</span><span style=\"color: brown;\">大台</span>出沒注意</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">連登忽然出現大量打手</span><br />\n<br />\n行動有鬼<br />\n=&gt;鬼嘅特徵<br />\n=&gt;掛住捉鬼<br />\n=&gt;互相猜忌<br />\n=&gt;限制行動<br />\n=&gt;出現糾察<br />\n=&gt;話人搞事<br />\n=&gt;分化大眾<br />\n=&gt;大台形成<br />\n<br />\n大家要留意呢排有好多人包括現場人士，議員，KOL限制你地嘅行動，講出似是而非，要保護邊個邊個唔好咁做，呢啲行為完全推翻呢2個月be water，兄弟爬山，不分化不割蓆嘅行動。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">小心解散軍。義士們，我相信你地！</span>"},{"pid":"2dc93cd0c1462e63d200977e13facf9fbbecfbc9","tid":1466580,"uid":240360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:49:42.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"3ca9a440e2bbd16fbde4eaa190acdb3b1e638f1d","tid":1466580,"uid":240360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:50:45.000Z","msg":"推到上宇宙"},{"pid":"6e5feee6a124accc4782981f1b7117e3280e6cc9","tid":1466580,"uid":165619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:51:56.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">今晚唔完美，可接受，但亦都要改善</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"6decf1ea61c74eba8f9b6f29d7eda6989440c879","tid":1466580,"uid":240360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:52:16.000Z","msg":"求下大家唔好分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d86797cd7e354c5a614ea806f4a5597b2248b065","tid":1466580,"uid":240360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:53:26.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"565aa3b7a15ca456c23050bfcc3205eae6a054e1","tid":1466580,"uid":240360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:55:10.000Z","msg":"集氣！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c6b9a4a771905c08ce682da6db1d7049e610138","tid":1466580,"uid":9845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:55:26.000Z","msg":"已使用最低武力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30d9b5044613ae1e86183d26664b2ff9cfd356c4","tid":1466580,"uid":271245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T16:57:25.000Z","msg